                           <div class="entire_tip">
<div class="tip_number">TIP 220</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            Dehydration or other complications due to excessive loss of fluid needs to be avoided in a baby or child who has diarrhea and/or vomiting. It can be life-threatening.
        </div>

</div>
